HEADWORD: Alcoholometry
<hw>Al`co*hol"om"e*try</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
process or method of ascertaining the proportion of pure alcohol which
spirituous liquors contain.</def>⟦br⟧
